msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroes_Desc"
msgid ""
"Zelda's voice spoke to you...\n"
"\n"
"She said that because you have tamed all\n"
"four Divine Beasts, you can now unlock\n"
"the powerful force hidden within.\n"
"\n"
"Head to the <1.se_co>Shrine of Resurrection<2.re_co> and\n"
"return the Sheikah Slate to its terminal."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroes_Finish"
msgid ""
"The power within prevailed! You proved your\n"
"worthiness to Monk Maz Koshia by completing\n"
"all of the Divine Beast Tamer's Trials. Your gift,\n"
"the <1.se_co>Master Cycle Zero<2.re_co>, can be found with your\n"
"Runes. After the trial, you met with Kass,\n"
"who sang the completed <3.se_co>Champions' Ballad<4.re_co>\n"
"for you. The song helped you recall the distant\n"
"day you were appointed as a Champion..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroes_Name"
msgid "EX The Champions' Ballad"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroes_Retire"
msgid ""
"After returning the Sheikah Slate to the terminal\n"
"in the Shrine of Resurrection, a mysterious\n"
"weapon appeared out of nowhere.\n"
"\n"
"You must use it to defeat all monsters at\n"
"four locations within the Great Plateau.\n"
"\n"
"The trial will begin again once you take hold\n"
"of the weapon that has returned to the\n"
"<1.se_co>Shrine of Resurrection<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

