msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroes_Step03"
msgid ""
"You completed the trials of the Great Plateau!\n"
"After conquering the last shrine, the One-Hit\n"
"Obliterator split into four glowing orbs and\n"
"scattered to different parts of Hyrule.\n"
"\n"
"There seems to be more to this trial...\n"
"What challenges await?\n"
"\n"
"Go to the areas marked on the map.\n"
"Locations remaining: <1.se_co><2.va><3.re_co>"
msgstr ""

