#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroes_Step04"
msgid ""
"In a realm of memory, you defeated the powerful\n"
"Phantom Ganons of the four Divine Beasts.\n"
"You have also completed the four trials\n"
"inscribed on the stone monument.\n"
"\n"
"But this trial is far from over.\n"
"\n"
"The door to the final trial in the <1.se_co>Shrine of \n"
"Resurrection<2.re_co> has opened. Return there\n"
"once more."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroes_Step05"
msgid ""
"When you returned the Sheikah Slate to the\n"
"terminal at the Shrine of Resurrection,\n"
"the room shook and descended.\n"
"\n"
"The shrine itself must have been designed to\n"
"play a part in the trial... Once you reached the\n"
"underground, an enormous space was revealed.\n"
"\n"
"Conquer the labyrinth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_BalladOfHeroes_Step06"
msgid ""
"You reached the deepest area of the\n"
"trial's labyrinth!\n"
"\n"
"Before you could report your completion of the\n"
"trial to Monk Maz Koshia, he rose before you\n"
"and the final trial started.\n"
"\n"
"Display your power by fighting Monk Maz Koshia\n"
"and proving you are worthy of mastering\n"
"a Divine Beast."
msgstr ""

